- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possibility as small-world networks are often used as a model for neural networks.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper involves analyzing the structure and properties of a specific type of graph.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possibility as the paper involves analyzing the spectra of matrices, which is a topic related to game theory.
